http://rst.gsfc.nasa.gov/Homepage/Homepage.html
3. Remote sensing and image interpretation, 5th edition, T.M. Lillesand, R.W. Kiefer. and J. W. Chipman, John Wiley & Sons, 2004
4. Introduction to remote sensing, 3rd edition, J.B. Campbell, Taylor & Francis, 2002.
5. Physical principles of remote sensing, 2nd edition, W.G. Rees, Cambridge University Press, 2001.
6. Introductory remote sensing - principles and concepts, 1st edition, P.J. Gibson and C.H. Power, Routledge, 2000.    

