備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 社會關懷
 Care for society.
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 宏觀地球科學專業知識及實務現象觀測
 Professional knowledge in Geosciences and practical surveys.
□ 地球科學專業文獻資料蒐集及實驗設計與整合操作規劃知能
 Professional literature in Geosciences, experimental design, and integrated knowledge of operation.
■ 地球科學專業知能與科技應用及量化檢測分析能力
 Professional knowledge in Geosciences and techniques for quantitative analysis.
□ 外語溝通能力
 Communication in foreign languages.
■ 團隊溝通、協調及領導能力
 Communication, negotiation and leadership on the team.
■ 整合應用地球科學產業專業科技知能及跨領域能力
 Integration technical skills and knowledge for geological industry and cross-disciplinary ability.
■ 積極?獵科學新知
 Explore new science knowledge.
■ 關懷自然環境及生態保育
 Care for natural environment and ecological conservation.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       This course is set to introduce students the fundamental concepts of remote sensing, as well as its limitation, characteristics and applications. This course provides the basic knowledge on satellite remote sensing, which is the prerequisite of another graduate-level course "Advanced topics in satellite remote sensing". 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Some video clips will be played in the class and an open discussionEncouraging students to ask questions and seek the answers as more as they canComplete some take-home questions and present the material they foundProviding a roadmap for further study in the general field of Remote Sensing 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction2Platform3Orbit4Sensor5Digital data6Ground truth7Midterm exam8Photogrammetry I9Photogrammetry II10Digital image processing I11Digital image processing II12Applications I13Applications II14Applications III15Applications IV16Geographic information system I17Geographic information system II18Final Exam 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


有關課程其他調查 Other Surveys of Courses
